{"type": "article", "id": 25816, "title": "月球灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-22T07:12:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140246c3nUrIbS5fClBjJz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">由 <a href=\"http://www.oscarlhermitte.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Oscar Lhermitte</a> 和 <a href=\"http://kudustudio.co/\" target=\"_blank\">Kudu.</a> 携手推出的这款科技感十足的月球灯是名副其实的“当技术遇上科学与艺术”的产物：使用了来自 NASA 的数据，无论是光线轨道还是月球微缩地形都做到了最大程度的精确。每一颗都在伦敦制作，并有独一无二的编号。中空的球体采用 3D 打印技术制成，光源则是利用了 LED 光圈。它不仅是一个具有科普意义的月球模型，也是一个照明灯具。参与 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1822742096/moon-the-most-accurate-lunar-globe\">Kickstarter</a> 的众筹，能以 500 欧元以内的价格购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140244BN6LYWbhye9tJuAH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140245RBQ7yTziFJfovrmK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140245AVs5y4tMwoRGBUkx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140245s4qVSgAWynr1CHj0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}